          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Scam Emails<\/p>",
            "heading_size": "2xl",
            "heading_size_desktop": "2xl",
            "heading_tracking_font": "tracking-0"
          }
        },
        "text_VFXf3H": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>It has come to our attention that a number of our customers have received emails from addresses impersonating ourselves, and sometimes requesting money. Please be aware that we will never contact you in this way, and all communications will come directly via telephone from our Customer Support team, or our official email address, help@remicachet.com.  <\/p><p>If you are concerned about any communications you have received from anyone claiming to be acting on the behalf of Remi Cachet, please use the contact form on our website to report them.<\/p><p>We value the safety and security of all our customers and want to ensure you are protected online at all times. Please help us by being vigilant against these online impersonators.<\/p>",
            "text_size": "sm",
            "text_size_desktop": "base"
          }
        }
      },
